隌字的汉语字典释义

[①]［àn］
［《廣韻》烏紺切，去勘，影。］
亦作“晻1”。亦作“隌1”。
(1)光线不足；不明亮。与“明”相对。
(2)夜；天黑。
(3)隐蔽，不显露；秘密，不公开。
(4)指隐蔽的地方。
(5)不显达。
(6)犹遮蔽。
(7)藏，包藏。
(8)犹言不知不觉。
(9)颜色幽深。
(10)谓失去光泽。
(11)谓视力差。
(12)犹默。参见“暗記”、“暗書”。
(13)昏乱；愚昧；不明白。
(14)黑暗。比喻社会腐败落后。
(15)见“暗藹”。
(16)通“窨”。参见“暗約”。

隌字的康熙字典解释

【戌集中】【阜字部】　隌； 康熙笔画：17； 页码：页1357第06
【廣韻】【集韻】?烏感切，音黤。【爾雅·釋言】隌，闇也。【註】隌然冥貌。【集韻】不明也。亦作暗。【玉篇】與晻同。　又【廣韻】【集韻】?於金切，音音。又【集韻】於禁切，音䕃。義?同。

Chinese dictionary definition of words
[①]［àn］
["Guang Yun" Wu Cang cut, go to survey, shadow. ]
Also known as "Dark 1". Also known as "隌1".
(1) Insufficient light; not bright. Contrast with "Ming".
(2) Night; dark.
(3) Concealed, not revealed; secret, not open.
(4) Refers to a hidden place.
(5) Not apparent.
(6) Still obscured.
(7) Hiding, hiding.
(8) Still talking unconsciously.
(9) The color is deep and deep.
(10) Said to lose luster.
(11) Said poor eyesight.
(12) Still Mo. See "Secret Record", "Secret Book".
(13) Confused; ignorant; don't understand.
(14) Darkness. A metaphor for social corruption and backwardness.
(15) See "Dark Ain".
(16) Through "scenting". See "dark appointment."
